      "cooked": "<h2>26 Maj, 2017. Fotot më pikante të ditës:</h2>\n<p><strong>Scarborough, Angli</strong><br>\n<strong>Policë të armatosur patrullojnë në plazhin South Bay.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/637a7f24f71cb47c2439dd7832b84cad524cc871.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/637a7f24f71cb47c2439dd7832b84cad524cc871\" title=\"2874.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/637a7f24f71cb47c2439dd7832b84cad524cc871.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"479\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/637a7f24f71cb47c2439dd7832b84cad524cc871_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">2874.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×735 130 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Taormina, Itali</strong><br>\n<strong>Trump bisedon me Theresa May, gjatë samitit të G7-s.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8c6b9a0063ac5a5e59e9bb6d3906cc5f77b0cbbf.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/8c6b9a0063ac5a5e59e9bb6d3906cc5f77b0cbbf\" title=\"3021.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8c6b9a0063ac5a5e59e9bb6d3906cc5f77b0cbbf.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"527\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8c6b9a0063ac5a5e59e9bb6d3906cc5f77b0cbbf_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">3021.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×807 169 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Mançester, Angli</strong><br>\n<strong>Njerëzit vazhdojnë homazhet për nder të viktimave të sulmit në Manchester.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/a76d3fd633546e7c2cef3d9b8ee3380ded8b3a77.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/a76d3fd633546e7c2cef3d9b8ee3380ded8b3a77\" title=\"3500 (1).jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/a76d3fd633546e7c2cef3d9b8ee3380ded8b3a77.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"555\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/a76d3fd633546e7c2cef3d9b8ee3380ded8b3a77_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">3500 (1).jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×851 182 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Gaza, Rripi i Gazës</strong><br>\n<strong>Një artist palestinez zbukuron një kafene para fillimit të muajit të Ramazanit.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/aeec0ea67a441fcf9d3a563047d637c672306b3e.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/aeec0ea67a441fcf9d3a563047d637c672306b3e\" title=\"5184.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/aeec0ea67a441fcf9d3a563047d637c672306b3e.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"533\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/aeec0ea67a441fcf9d3a563047d637c672306b3e_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"